            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced carrot</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until it's beginning to soften</p><p>Once beginning to soften, add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong>, <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>ginger</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 2-3 min</p>",
